      "body" : "This makes sense as a default; but what if you want to run a bitcoin node as a hidden service? this works using port redirection, so you need a listening port *on localhost* at least.\r\n\r\nI propose: Providing explicit `-port` argument overrides `-nolisten`.\r\n\r\nAnother option would be to listen on localhost only when on tor.\r\n",
